item.title: I Need help on how to get rid of the 10mill in varrock on my source fr33sc4p3
item.dc:creator: @Goodoo_dolls Goodoo dolls
item.description:
@Goodoo_dolls wrote:

if you have itemspawnpoints.java open that press ctrl+f type in 995 and delete it it should look like this…

ItemHandler.addItem(995, 3256, 3430, 19999999, ItemHandler.globalItemController[i], false); // coins1

ItemHandler.addItem(995, 3256, 3427, 19999999, ItemHandler.globalItemController[i], false); // coins2

ItemHandler.addItem(995, 3242, 3429, 19999999, ItemHandler.globalItemController[i], false); // coins3

ItemHandler.addItem(995, 3240, 3433, 19999999, ItemHandler.globalItemController[i], false); // coins4

something like that
